{"tid":1124262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"放針狗真係痴能線！食個叉燒飯都搵命搏！","createTime":"2019-04-25T02:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T02:51:19.000Z","uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4339cf5aa3bce5507ec955d071d3eca301b56926","tid":1124262,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"網民熱話：食叉燒飯險吞鐵針 事主嘆食飯都要搵命博<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190425/photo/bkn-20190425093035375-0425_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190425095034\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190425%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190425093035375-0425_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190425095034&h=c2228ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒味飯是不少港人的午飯首選，惟大快朵頤時亦不能掉以輕心！昨日（24日）有人食用叉燒飯時，發現叉燒上有不明針狀物體。拔出細看，竟與針筒上的針頭十分相似，令食客不寒而慄，直斥：「食個叉燒飯都要搵命博？」<br />\n<br />\n網民Andy Poo 在 Facebook 群組「Fanling 粉嶺」上分享恐怖經歷，指食叉燒飯時食出異物，其外露部分十分尖銳，他以手指輕觸，竟發現是一根長度約姆指頭的針。他留言直斥燒味店收買人命：「咁長嘅針都發現唔到，好彩我望到唔對路，拿手指摸落去。」他續稱，異物的材質是鐵，回想自己差點誤食「鐵針」，不禁高呼：「唔係講笑，謀殺呀依家？」<br />\n<br />\n有網民根據相片內的「鐵針」外型和大小，推測其「本體」應是針筒的「針頭」，不禁質疑源頭來自供應商：「係咪幫啲豬打針嗰陣漏低？」「應該係隻豬仲在生嘅時候，打激素之類嘅針筒頭。」有網民擔心食安問題，建議事主向食環署反映事件，「報食環，人命攸關」、「報食環處理，取回公道！」<br />\n<br />\n東網致電有關食店查詢，職員表示不知道有鐵針事件，「無啦啦點會有支針呢」，又反問「點解佢（食客）有問題都冇返嚟講嘅？」至於會否是貨源問題，她則表示「真係唔知道」，以前亦未曾發生類似事件。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nPoon NY：咁離譜！<br />\nMaurice Kan：報食環啦！<br />\nRay Tsang：唔少酒樓／燒味舖都係攞貨賣，唔好講到佢有心放落去咁。"},{"pid":"ce1c01e58c819d2fc78f09329c9f2c7c56694ee0","tid":1124262,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:38:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190425/bkn-20190425093035375-0425_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190425%2Fbkn-20190425093035375-0425_00822_001.html&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=8224067b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190425/bkn-20190425093035375-0425_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a44a784c23cf2a7baf9f116ab1b71d4db11a8107","tid":1124262,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e73c151ff23b22cab0c0c4eeba3540aad30329","tid":1124262,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:40:13.000Z","msg":"放到粉嶺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a971e9aa0a4740c19533614367f6702a9163efc","tid":1124262,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:40:21.000Z","msg":"@N賓"},{"pid":"53b82f6bfcbb8482487dd27577a4778cfb040584","tid":1124262,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"樓主嬲到放針"},{"pid":"ff7a249b2af39922df4497bff6c5a7db2b44a76d","tid":1124262,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:48:21.000Z","msg":"n賓淨係放座位<br />\n唔係佢做"},{"pid":"1b93d646c182378ab1d54035a33d95974f518b83","tid":1124262,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b82f6bfcbb8482487dd27577a4778cfb040584","tid":1124262,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"樓主嬲到放針"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"死痢狗, 我屌你老母"}]}